## Quality Check

Run quality checks for {{ project_name }}.

### Steps

1. **Lint check**: Verify code quality and style
2. **Format check**: Ensure consistent code formatting
3. **Tests**: Run test suite

### Execution

{% if project_type == "python-cli" or project_type == "python-lib" %}
```bash
# Lint
uvx ruff check src/

# Format check
uvx ruff format --check src/

# Tests
uv run pytest
```
{% elif project_type == "node-frontend" %}
```bash
# Lint
npm run lint

# Format check
npm run format:check

# Tests
npm test
```
{% elif project_type == "infrastructure" %}
```bash
# Terraform validate
terraform validate

# Ansible lint (if applicable)
ansible-lint

# Check formatting
terraform fmt -check
```
{% elif project_type == "documentation" or project_type == "lab" %}
```bash
# Build docs (validates structure)
mkdocs build --strict

# Lint markdown
npx markdownlint docs/
```
